### DTE Chile App - API Test Collection
### Use this file with VS Code REST Client extension

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@baseApiUrl = https://api.baseapi.cl/v1
@apiKey = your_baseapi_api_key_here
@token = your_token_here

### Local API - Generate PDF
POST {{baseUrl}}/generate-pdf
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tipoDTE": 33,
  "folio": 12345,
  "fechaEmision": "2026-07-16",
  "formaPago": 1,
  "rutEmisor": "12345678-9",
  "razonSocialEmisor": "Proveedor SPA",
  "giroEmisor": "Comercio al por mayor",
  "direccionEmisor": "Calle Principal 123",
  "comunaEmisor": "Santiago",
  "rutReceptor": "87654321-0",
  "razonSocialReceptor": "Mi Empresa LTDA",
  "items": [
    {
      "nroLinea": 1,
      "nombreItem": "Producto A",
      "cantidad": 2,
      "unidad": "UN",
      "precioUnitario": 50000,
      "montoItem": 100000
    }
  ],
  "montoNeto": 100000,
  "tasaIVA": 19,
  "iva": 19000,
  "montoTotal": 119000,
  "ted": "<TED>...</TED>"
}

### BaseAPI - Authenticate
POST {{baseApiUrl}}/auth
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rut": "12345678-9",
  "clave": "your_sii_password"
}

### BaseAPI - Get DTE List (requires token)
GET {{baseApiUrl}}/dte/recibidos?periodo=2026-07
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}

### BaseAPI - Get DTE XML (requires token)
GET {{baseApiUrl}}/dte/recibidos/12345
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}

### BaseAPI - Get Contributor Data (requires token)
GET {{baseApiUrl}}/contribuyente/datos-receptor?rut=12345678-9
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}

### BaseAPI - Get RCV (Registro de Compras) (requires token)
GET {{baseApiUrl}}/rcv?periodo=2026-07
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}
